stages.\n\nNext: Payload Valid?","width":280,"height":232,"color":7},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[-6,520],"id":"8103b512-b67b-10f5-8fd8-3efbd3b6476a","name":"Note: Stamp & Shape Request"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Payload Valid?\n\nTwo-way gate on `={{ $json.requestId }}`. TRUE continues the happy path, FALSE takes the alternate branch.\n\nPorts: ①→ Remove Duplicate Requests · ②→ Record Rejected Input","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[318,520],"id":"79981fe2-33b3-dade-8cc0-a2fc77b3c5c7","name":"Note: Payload Valid?"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Record Rejected Input\n\ngoogleSheets — `contact` operation against the connected account.\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · 🔑 Google OAuth2 / service account","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[318,1030],"id":"a02afd5d-593e-3482-9f06-cb3217b8f258","name":"Note: Record Rejected Input"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Remove Duplicate Requests\n\nDrops duplicates within this run (compared on `requestId`).\n\nNext: Enrich — Primary Provider","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[642,520],"id":"47b89890-fd0a-8db8-c62d-3b4612a370ca","name":"Note: Remove Duplicate Requests"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Enrich — Primary Provider\n\nGET https://enrichment.example.com/v2/lookup — retries 3× with backoff on failure.\n\nPorts: ①→ Primary Hit? · ②→ Capture Failure Context\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · ⚠ failures exit via the error rail · 🔑 API key / bearer for the target API","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[966,520],"id":"e337864e-1d36-2474-a70f-fb42cca4e4e0","name":"Note: Enrich — Primary Provider"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Primary Hit?\n\nTwo-way gate on `={{ $json.company || $json.name }}`. TRUE continues the happy path, FALSE takes the alternate branch.\n\nPorts: ①→ Merge Enrichment Paths · ②→ Enrich — Fallback Provider","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[1290,520],"id":"8ecef6d6-d1c8-4a46-63ee-a1d955f747b1","name":"Note: Primary Hit?"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Enrich — Fallback Provider\n\nGET https://fallback-enrich.example.com/v1/person — retries 3× with backoff on failure.\n\nPorts: ①→ Merge Enrichment Paths · ②→ Capture Failure Context\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · ⚠ failures exit via the error rail · 🔑 API key / bearer for the target API","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[1614,1000],"id":"a6d65fb7-75e8-837f-31d2-ca0ddca35673","name":"Note: Enrich — Fallback Provider"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Merge Enrichment Paths\n\nRejoins 2 branches into one stream (mode: append) so downstream logic runs once.\n\nNext: Score Enriched Records","width":280,"height":232,"color":7},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[2262,520],"id":"ab964950-c063-965c-0120-9dcafba99bd3","name":"Note: Merge Enrichment Paths"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Score Enriched Records\n\nCustom JavaScript: Score each request 0-100 from simple heuristics\n\nNext: Upsert into HubSpot","width":280,"height":232,"color":7},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[3234,520],"id":"5ad2999c-7db7-413d-f3ee-99dcc2e62b5f","name":"Note: Score Enriched Records"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Upsert into HubSpot\n\nhubspot — `contact` operation against the connected account.\n\nPorts: ①→ Hot Lead? · ②→ Capture Failure Context\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · ⚠ failures exit via the error rail · 🔑 HubSpot private-app token","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[3558,520],"id":"b48a9d45-7c22-b51d-9476-a572c18da072","name":"Note: Upsert into HubSpot"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Hot Lead?\n\nTwo-way gate on `={{ $json.score >= 80 }}`. TRUE continues the happy path, FALSE takes the alternate branch.\n\nPorts: ①→ Ping Owner Immediately · ②→ Serialize Run Output (CSV)","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[3882,520],"id":"800b6144-1f82-21bf-2cc2-e2d92f12a155","name":"Note: Hot Lead?"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Ping Owner Immediately\n\nslack — `action` operation against the connected account.\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · ⚠ failures exit via the error rail · 🔑 Slack OAuth2","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[4206,280],"id":"e454ea86-06e3-b217-aec8-8e63481da40a","name":"Note: Ping Owner Immediately"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Serialize Run Output (CSV)\n\nSerializes items to a CSV binary file.\n\nNext: Archive Row Snapshot","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[4530,520],"id":"b6dae966-a462-8983-256c-768092ec9498","name":"Note: Serialize Run Output (CSV)"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Archive Row Snapshot\n\nairtable — `create` operation against the connected account.\n\nPorts: ①→ Stamp Completion Time · ②→ Capture Failure Context\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · ⚠ failures exit via the error rail · 🔑 Airtable PAT","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[4854,520],"id":"9b1bb557-fd86-9cae-8e07-a41c74920c47","name":"Note: Archive Row Snapshot"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Stamp Completion Time\n\nStamps `completedAt` with the current time for auditing.\n\nNext: Persist Run Metadata","width":280,"height":232,"color":7},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[5178,520],"id":"b433789b-13aa-430e-debc-15d27d22efd1","name":"Note: Stamp Completion Time"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Persist Run Metadata\n\nSaves key fields onto the execution record — searchable later in n8n's execution list.\n\nNext: Summarize Run Stats","width":280,"height":232,"color":7},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[5502,520],"id":"66af506f-9ea2-c649-2bd1-6bfc6167551a","name":"Note: Persist Run Metadata"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Summarize Run Stats\n\nShapes the item: writes `runAt`, `itemCount`, `status`. Keeps the schema explicit between stages.\n\nNext: Append Audit Row (Google Sheets)","width":280,"height":232,"color":7},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[5826,520],"id":"9a33fe84-40b2-c017-8f83-b851afdff285","name":"Note: Summarize Run Stats"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Append Audit Row (Google Sheets)\n\ngoogleSheets — `append` operation against the connected account.\n\nPorts: ①→ Send Summary to Slack · ②→ Capture Failure Context\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · ⚠ failures exit via the error rail · 🔑 Google OAuth2 / service account","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[6150,520],"id":"ede568ab-400f-873e-d8d2-d823d10d5e16","name":"Note: Append Audit Row (Google Sheets)"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Send Summary to Slack\n\nslack — `action` operation against the connected account.\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · ⚠ failures exit via the error rail · 🔑 Slack OAuth2","width":280,"height":232,"color":4},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[6474,520],"id":"93a9607e-3e4d-8d2d-dd15-5c52049fbefa","name":"Note: Send Summary to Slack"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Capture Failure Context\n\nShapes the item: writes `failedNode`, `errorMessage`, `workflow`. Keeps the schema explicit between stages.\n\nNext: Escalate Failure to Slack","width":280,"height":232,"color":3},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[5826,1540],"id":"ace5e2de-6b6b-632d-6071-ecca8930bd3f","name":"Note: Capture Failure Context"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Escalate Failure to Slack\n\nslack — `action` operation against the connected account.\n\nNext: Park in Dead-Letter Queue\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · 🔑 Slack OAuth2","width":280,"height":232,"color":3},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[6150,1540],"id":"eced208f-2d59-2000-e3ee-ad0c1e8c0e19","name":"Note: Escalate Failure to Slack"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Park in Dead-Letter Queue\n\nhubspot — `contact` operation against the connected account.\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · 🔑 HubSpot private-app token","width":280,"height":232,"color":3},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[6474,1540],"id":"1860f7b9-fdb6-ac85-963e-df0b73add696","name":"Note: Park in Dead-Letter Queue"},{"parameters":{"content":"# Enrich company profiles with HubSpot and HTTP / REST API end to end for Multi-Tool Agent (01461)\n\n**Pattern:** Data Enrichment · **Level:** Production · **Trigger:** Scheduled\n\n## What it does\nEnrich company profiles with HubSpot and HTTP / REST API end to end for Multi-Tool Agent (01461). It runs automatically on a schedule.\n\n## Why it exists\nManual multi-tool agent is slow and error-prone; this workflow makes the process repeatable, monitored and hands-off, with failures surfaced instead of silently lost.\n\n## Main flow\nWeekly Schedule → Stamp & Shape Request → Payload Valid? → Remove Duplicate Requests → Enrich — Primary Provider → Primary Hit? → Merge Enrichment Paths → …\n\n## Use it for\n- Teams that want to data enrichment without manual effort\n- Anyone automating multi-tool agent in ai\n- Replacing a fragile manual process with a reliable workflow\n\n## You get\n- Saves hours of manual work each week\n- Standardizes the process every time\n- Runs 24/7 in the background\n\n## Before first run\nConnect credentials: API key / bearer for the target API; Airtable PAT; Google OAuth2 / service account; HubSpot private-app token; Slack OAuth2.\nFollow the color key: 🟦 entry · 🟪 AI · 🟫 actions · ⬜ utilities · 🟩 outputs · 🟥 error rail.\nEach node has its own doc card underneath — read those before editing.","width":480,"height":900},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[-830,80],"id":"60e0d7eb-d77d-e0de-8744-8e7efcdafca3","name":"📘 Workflow Overview"},{"parameters":{"content":"## 🛟 Error handling & retries\n\nExternal calls retry **3× with 2s backoff**. Anything still failing exits through its node's error output into the red error rail → context is captured and the on-call channel is alerted. Failures are also parked in a dead-letter queue for replay. Set an n8n **Error Workflow** in settings as the final safety net.","width":360,"height":260,"color":3},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[-230,-260],"id":"904d1778-d46c-12fe-8b7f-a51126d484c1","name":"🛟 Error handling & retries"},{"parameters":{"content":"## 🧹 Data quality\n\nDedupe/diff steps make re-runs safe: the same input twice will not create duplicate records. If you change the key fields, clear n8n's dedupe memory (node → 'Clear stored keys') before the next run.","width":360,"height":260,"color":1},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[190,-260],"id":"ab49d221-fded-0205-a05e-afa7e478ca99","name":"🧹 Data quality"},{"parameters":{"content":"## 🛠 Customize me\n\nQuick wins: point the data nodes at your own accounts (see 🔑 lines on each card), adjust the trigger cadence, and tune thresholds/labels to your multi-tool agent process. Every node card explains its role — safe to extend at any marked branch.","width":360,"height":260,"color":4},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[610,-260],"id":"e37f7bda-e4d0-bb01-4de0-0b9c20ada08a","name":"🛠 Customize me"}],"connections":{"Weekly Schedule":{"main":[[{"node":"Stamp & Shape Request","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Stamp & Shape Request":{"main":[[{"node":"Payload Valid?","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Payload Valid?":{"main":[[{"node":"Remove Duplicate Requests","type":"main","index":0}],[{"node":"Record Rejected Input","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Remove Duplicate Requests":{"main":[[{"node":"Enrich — Primary Provider","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Enrich — Primary Provider":{"main":[[{"node":"Primary Hit?","type":"main","index":0}],[{"node":"Capture Failure Context","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Primary Hit?":{"main":[[{"node":"Merge Enrichment Paths","type":"main","index":0}],[{"node":"Enrich — Fallback Provider","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Enrich — Fallback Provider":{"main":[[{"node":"Merge Enrichment Paths","type":"main","index":1}],[{"node":"Capture Failure Context","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Merge Enrichment Paths":{"main":[[{"node":"Score Enriched Records","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Score Enriched Records":{"main":[[{"node":"Upsert into HubSpot","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Upsert into HubSpot":{"main":[[{"node":"Hot Lead?","type":"main","index":0}],[{"node":"Capture Failure Context","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Hot Lead?":{"main":[[{"node":"Ping Owner Immediately","type":"main","index":0}],[{"node":"Serialize Run Output (CSV)","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Serialize Run Output (CSV)":{"main":[[{"node":"Archive Row Snapshot","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Archive Row Snapshot":{"main":[[{"node":"Stamp Completion Time","type":"main","index":0}],[{"node":"Capture Failure Context","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Stamp Completion Time":{"main":[[{"node":"Persist Run Metadata","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Persist Run Metadata":{"main":[[{"node":"Summarize Run Stats","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Summarize Run Stats":{"main":[[{"node":"Append Audit Row (Google Sheets)","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Append Audit Row (Google Sheets)":{"main":[[{"node":"Send Summary to Slack","type":"main","index":0}],[{"node":"Capture Failure Context","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Capture Failure Context":{"main":[[{"node":"Escalate Failure to Slack","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Escalate Failure to Slack":{"main":[[{"node":"Park in Dead-Letter Queue","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Ping Owner Immediately":{"main":[[],[{"node":"Capture Failure Context","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Send Summary to Slack":{"main":[[],[{"node":"Capture Failure Context","type":"main","index":0}]]}},"active":false,"settings":{"executionOrder":"v1"},"meta":{"templateCredsSetupCompleted":false},"tags":[],"pinData":{},"versionId":"c6a0abc5-d67a-408a-be96-9c6af256c456","id":"FDX01461"}